1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 19=

11
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,079
You're not Jiang Yao.

12
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,680
Who are you?

13
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,480
Forgot me already?

14
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,359
Senior?

15
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,439
Senior.

16
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,439
Senior, let's talk this out.

17
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,239
I heard Su Wubing

18
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:31,519
pulled the divine sword.

19
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,640
Yes. He's ruining everything.

20
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,840
So, he's the ancient Immortal King.

21
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,120
Immortal King?

22
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,959
Su Wubing is the Immortal King?

23
00:01:57,799 --> 00:02:00,760
What else explains how strong he is?

24
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:04,400
Is there a woman

25
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,159
named Lin Ningxue with him?

26
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,400
Yes.

27
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,560
Ever since he showed up,

28
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,680
he's helped her every time.

29
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:18,560
Then her curse hasn't been lifted yet.

30
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,159
Senior.

31
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:21,639
This...

32
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,159
If Su Wubing is the Immortal King,

33
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,240
can you beat him?

34
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,680
No!

35
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,919
A mere mortal dares question me?

36
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,240
Senior, I'm just looking out for you.

37
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:43,319
Immortal King or not,

38
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:45,319
he's still in a mortal body.

39
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:52,039
Maybe this time
I can even take two immortal souls.

40
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,360
Senior.

41
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,479
As long as you eliminate him,

42
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:59,199
I will follow you to the end.

43
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,400
Before I came out of seclusion,

44
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:09,080
capture Lin Ningxue
to lure out the Immortal King.

45
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:10,919
Yes.

46
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,479
I'll do as you command.

47
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,800
Senior.

48
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,319
Senior.

49
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,759
Mr. Gu.

50
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,080
You still have the nerve to speak?

51
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,759
Su Wubing.

52
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:43,560
Let's see how you get out of this one.

53
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,759
I'm finally going to win.

54
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,360
This aura...

55
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,800
It's the ancient Demon Clan.

56
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,280
Who are you?

57
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,000
Immortal King,

58
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,439
once I leave seclusion,

59
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:19,360
I'll settle the score with you myself

60
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:23,399
and take your soul
to fulfill the Demon Clan's plan.

61
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:41,160
Did Wubing turn you down?

62
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,600
W-W-Who got rejected?

63
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,759
I was just bored and stopped by.

64
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:51,319
Sure. Whatever you say.

65
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,360
And...

66
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:57,639
if you want to know
about the two of them,

67
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,720
I can tell you.

68
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,160
I've got nothing better to do anyway.

69
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,920
Fine.

70
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,120
So,

71
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,120
Wubing and the Holy Maiden

72
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,879
are made for each other.

73
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,360
Forget breaking them up...

74
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,480
Even a temporary separation

75
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,279
is out of the question.

76
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:39,680
Grandpa,

77
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,600
even if you're defending him,

78
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,680
you don't have to make up
something that outrageous.

79
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,720
Believe it or not,

80
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:53,319
everything I said is true.

81
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,360
Fine, fine.

82
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,879
Even if you told me

83
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:00,720
you've been alive since ancient times,

84
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,560
I'd believe that too, okay?

85
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,959
If you

86
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:10,720
truly admire Wubing,

87
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:15,000
staying by his side

88
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:17,800
isn't a bad choice.

89
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,920
Who knows... maybe one day

90
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,000
he'll change his mind.

91
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:28,199
(Oh, no. Grandpa's spent his whole life
healing people.)

92
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:31,639
(Don't tell me he's gone senile now.)

93
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,040
Still so reckless.

94
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:03,439
(Shan Martial Hall.
We need to talk. Come.)

95
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,079
(Shan Yingying?)

96
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,199
(Can't she just call?)

97
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,759
All of you, out.

98
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,720
Let's fight again.

99
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,040
Again?

100
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,800
You used spiritual power last time.

101
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,879
If you win this time,

102
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,319
the martial hall is yours.

103
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,920
If you lose, keep doing chores here.

104
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,680
Win or lose,

105
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,399
I'm still part of this place.

106
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,439
Suit yourself.

107
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,439
Bring it on.

108
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:06,639
Without spiritual power,
you're nothing special.

109
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,839
Why does this always happen?

110
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,360
Fine, I surrender.

111
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,199
This is our family heirloom
spirit stone.

112
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,720
Every head of the family

113
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,680
uses it to cultivate.

114
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:34,320
Ningxue told me about you.

115
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,559
I thought it might help you.

116
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,279
This is...

117
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:44,039
the stone used to forge
the Heavenly God Sword.

118
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,799
Thanks.

119
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,879
No need.

120
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,799
I just want to know

121
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,600
are you really the Immortal King?

122
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:01,679
Fine, keep your secrets.

123
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,720
I also want to ask you

124
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,320
do you remember

125
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,360
what you told me at the hotel that day?

126
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:13,080
You said if Ningxue were in danger

127
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,799
and saving her
meant sacrificing yourself,

128
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:16,559
you'd do it.

129
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:17,960
Is that true?

130
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,039
Yes.

131
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:26,559
You really are different

132
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:27,600
from any other man I've met.

133
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,759
I hope you mean what you say.

134
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,639
I don't understand
the Heavenly Dao's curse,

135
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,960
but Ningxue may look tough
on the outside,

136
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,960
but inside, she's barely holding on.

137
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,720
Don't let her down.

138
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:48,759
Thanks.

139
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:51,840
Wait.

140
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,559
One more thing.

141
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,559
How many wives can an immortal have?

142
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,879
W-W-Who's there?

143
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:35,720
Maybe I'm just too tense.

144
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,399
Guard the entrance.

145
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:48,919
No one gets in.

146
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:49,519
Yes.

147
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,879
Miss Lin,

148
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:07,440
let's make up for our wedding night.

149
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,159
What?

150
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,919
You have something to say?

151
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,600
Get lost.

152
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,759
Get lost?

153
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,919
Don't touch me.

154
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,320
Don't touch you?

155
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,200
You're like a lamb to the slaughter now.

156
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:34,919
If you touch me again,

157
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:37,759
Su Wubing won't let you off!

158
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,159
Su Wubing?

159
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:48,519
Even he couldn't find you.

160
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:03,200
Once I'm done with you,
I'll send you back.

161
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,639
Then you can

162
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:07,600
reunite with him underground.

163
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,840
Don't touch me!

164
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,559
Get off me!

165
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,120
Don't touch me!

166
00:13:37,291 --> 00:13:41,394
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

167
00:13:41,394 --> 00:13:46,114
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

168
00:13:46,114 --> 00:13:50,994
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

169
00:13:50,994 --> 00:13:56,114
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

170
00:13:56,114 --> 00:14:00,514
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

171
00:14:00,514 --> 00:14:05,194
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

172
00:14:05,194 --> 00:14:10,594
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

173
00:14:10,594 --> 00:14:16,988
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

